  <entry>
    <title>使用next主题踩到的坑</title>
    <link href="https://gypsophila123.github.io/2020/10/28/err-NexT/"/>
    <id>https://gypsophila123.github.io/2020/10/28/err-NexT/</id>
    <published>2020-10-28T05:18:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-29T04:52:49.518Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>文章内容仅供参考，如有踩坑概不负责，下载next主题的时间：2020-10-23（在此之前GitHub上的最近更新时间是9-2）</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="下载链接错误"><a href="#下载链接错误" class="headerlink" title="下载链接错误"></a>下载链接错误</h1><p>通过别人的博客知道hexo支持一个非常好看的next主题，我当然不会错过。Google之后发现NexT官方文档居然是全中文的，这下可把我乐坏了，美滋滋！然而事情没这么简单，<strong>以下为官方文档原话</strong></p><blockquote><p>Hexo 安装主题的方式非常简单，只需要将主题文件拷贝至站点目录的 <code>themes</code> 目录下， 然后修改下配置文件即可。具体到 NexT 来说，安装步骤如下。</p><p>$ cd your-hexo-site<br>$ git clone <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next</a> themes/next</p></blockquote><p>看到这个路径在github上，出于习惯我点进去看了一眼。不得了，最近一次更新还是在去年初，readme上一个迁移提示，大意是说这个仓库不更新了，想用新版本需要去新的仓库（链接：<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">NexT v6 and v7 </a>）。所以说，<strong>如果需要下载最新版本的NexT主题的命令应该是</strong></p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:<span class="regexp">//gi</span>thub.com<span class="regexp">/theme-next/</span>hexo-theme-<span class="keyword">next</span> themes/<span class="keyword">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里我就留了个心眼，要时刻注意不被这个官方文档坑</p><h1 id="设置语言为中文"><a href="#设置语言为中文" class="headerlink" title="设置语言为中文"></a>设置语言为中文</h1><p><strong>在NexT的官方文档中是这样说的：</strong></p><blockquote><p>编辑 <strong>站点配置文件</strong>， 将 <code>language</code> 设置成你所需要的语言。建议明确设置你所需要的语言，例如选用简体中文，配置如下：</p><p>language: zh-Hans</p></blockquote><img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028132326518.png" class><p>然而实际上新版本中zh-Hans已经改为了zh-CN</p><img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028132159541.png" class><p><strong>所以使用简体中文应该设置：</strong></p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">language:</span> <span class="built_in">zh</span>-CN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="侧边社交栏链接"><a href="#侧边社交栏链接" class="headerlink" title="侧边社交栏链接"></a>侧边社交栏链接</h1><p><strong>官方文档如下：</strong></p><img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028165632286.png" class><p>实际在使用中应该这样</p><figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">social</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">GitHub</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//github.com/Gypsophila123 || fab fa-github</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">G-Mail</span>: yuanjie15115580021<span class="variable">@gmail</span>.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Weibo</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//weibo.com/yourname || fab fa-weibo</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Google</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//plus.google.com/yourname || fab fa-google</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Twitter</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//twitter.com/yourname || fab fa-twitter</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">#FB</span> <span class="attribute">Page</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//www.facebook.com/yourname || fab fa-facebook</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">StackOverflow</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//stackoverflow.com/yourname || fab fa-stack-overflow</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">YouTube</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//youtube.com/yourname || fab fa-youtube</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Instagram</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//instagram.com/yourname || fab fa-instagram</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Skype</span>: <span class="attribute">skype</span>:yourname?call|chat || fab fa-skype</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">social_icons</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">enable</span>: true # 是否显示图标</span><br><span class="line">  # Icon Mappings</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">GitHub</span>: github</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">icons_only</span>: false # 仅显示图标</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028165537958.png" class><h1 id="模板渲染错误"><a href="#模板渲染错误" class="headerlink" title="模板渲染错误"></a>模板渲染错误</h1><p>最初遇到这个问题的时候，我人是懵逼的，server上冒出一大堆红色的代码，让我以为自己造成了什么不可弥补的错误。根据提示，我一路找到了<strong>my_blog\node_modules\nunjucks\src</strong>路径的environment.js文件，然后看到了这句话，搞不懂搞不懂。</p><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// <span class="doctag">TODO:</span> this is actually a bug in the compiled template (because waterfall</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// tasks are both not passing errors up the chain of callbacks AND are not</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// causing a return from the top-most render function). But fixing that</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// will require a more substantial change to the compiler.</span></span><br><span class="line">    以下为Google翻译</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//TODO：这实际上是已编译模板中的错误（因为瀑布</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//任务都没有在回调链中传递错误，并且没有</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//导致从最顶层的渲染函数返回。 但是修复</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//将需要对编译器进行更实质性的更改。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际上根据我的经验，这可能只是某个地方标点符号打错了，某个参数非法了，亦或者不可识别的字符。为了防止这种情况。我建议每改一点都去刷新网页，看一下server界面的情况，不要想当然的一路改下去最后再查看，不然很难定位问题。</p><blockquote><p>tip：目前我的网页主界面已经找不到分类和标签的按钮了，因为我觉得极简非常的简洁美观大方。<del>我实在找不到哪里有错误了（捂脸）。</del></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;文章内容仅供参考，如有踩坑概不负责，下载next主题的时间：2020-10-23（在此之前GitHub上的最近更新时间是9-2）&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
